              <div class="views-field views-field-title"> 
               <span class="field-content"><a href="http://news.psu.edu/story/346419/2015/02/26/academics/lindberg-selected-speaker-tedxpsu-2015">Lindberg selected as speaker for TEDxPSU 2015</a></span> 
              </div> 
              <div class="views-field views-field-body"> 
               <div class="field-content">
                <span class="post-date"><span class="date-display-single" property="dc:date" datatype="xsd:dateTime" content="2015-02-26T09:26:00-05:00">2/26/15</span></span>
                <p>TEDxPSU 2015 has selected Darla Lindberg, Penn State’s Stuckeman School Chair of Design Innovation and professor of architecture, as one of the speakers for the Sunday, March 1, exposition of ideas.</p> 
